Corporate Events
Team Building with a lot of FUN!
Mission “FUN”:  A Team Based scavenger hunt across all of Family Fun Town.
Arcade Madness: A Team Arcade Face-off where teams compete head-to-head playing arcade games like Mario Kart, Power Roll, Whack N’ Win, and Ice Ball.  As the points add up, the competitive team spirit shines through until all the points are tabulated and the team with the highest collective point total WINS!   There is a focus on teamwork, strategy, and communication skills.
Field Trip & Summer Camps
From a round of Mini Golf for the winning class or
safety
patrol, to the end of the year celebration Family Fun Town has you covered.
Community Groups
Join your group for a fun filled round of Mini Golf, or a race to the finish line on the Go Karts.
Private Parties
From a family reunion to renting out the entire facility for a private party, Family Fun Town can customise a package to fit your needs.
Spirit Nights
PTA/PTO and other school or church organization, schedule a spirit night at Family Fun Town and recieve special attraction pricing, and a donation of up to 25% of the events sales.
Golf Tournaments
Reserve the Mini Golf Course for your own private fundraiser mini golf tournament.

About Park
It is our goal to make your Family Fun Town experience as friendly, comfortable, and FUN as possible. Volusia County’s Family Fun Town is a great place for all ages to enjoy our exciting family friendly entertainment complex, including: Birthday Parties, Mini Golf, Go-Karts, Batting Cages, Arcade Games and many more fun filled family attractions.  We take great pride in the appearance of our facility as well as the level of service that we provide. Our entire staff is dedicated to providing an excellent Family Fun Town experience.
